title: Star Wars 01-12 + FCBD (2013) (Digital)
description: This torrent collects Star Wars issues 01-12, the latest series from Dark Horse Comics. This is the series that takes place directly after the Battle of Yavin (or following the events of "A New Hope"). This is NOT "The Star Wars" which is an alternate retelling of the SW Trilogy using Lucas' old scripts. Just to avoid any confusion! I also included the FCBD edition since it was in the original torrent that I've supplemented here. I will also post Star Wars Legacy 1-10 soon, for those interested, since issues 8 and 9 of that series are not on TPB. All credit to Cypher Empire for the scans. Enjoy and please seed, thanks! :-)
